The National Energy Regulator of South Africa has approved an 18-point-six-five-percent electricity tariff hike for Eskom. eNCA's Heidi Giokos has more. #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - In just a few months you will see a big jump in your electricity bill. The National Energy Regulator of South Africa has approved an 18.65% electricity tariff hike for Eskom. READ: Nersa approves 18.65% tariff increase for Eskom The tariff hikes will come into effect in April with yet another increase expected for 2024. Most businesses and South Africans at large have rejected the price increase. eNCA's Heidi Giokos has more details in the video above.